metadata.description: The Loser Club Mixtape Volume I is the genesis NFT to be minted by The Outsider Collective - a group of creatives spanning the disciplines of art and music to build a web3-first ecosystem founded on the values of creativity, community and collaboration. The mixtape has been a collaborative project open to holders of Loser Club NFTs, resulting in a final tracklist of 12 songs as voted for by the Loser Club community. The cover art features all Losers whose submissions made the mixtape, and was drawn by the Loser King himself, J’von (aka Catman) - artist for the official Loser Club project. Track List Loser Theme Song - Omotayo (prod. Omotayo) Moon - paperhandpapi & GRL (prod. Pilot Kid) NFT.NYC - Leo Pastel & GRL (prod. GRL) Bossfight - Bad Alphabet, paperhandpapi & werb (prod. sayhellojordan) Weekend - Leo Pastel (prod. werb and Leo Pastel) Sweep The Floor - paperhandpapi & werb (prod. GRL) Hey Loser - Jonny October (prod. Jonny October) Mind Trip - TBlock (prod. Dopant Beats) Dreaming - Sergio, Ley & jo.ao (prod. Sergio) sing the blues - werb (prod. werb) Loser Theme Song Remix - Omotayo, Profit & werb (prod. werb) Papi's Outro (prod. fresh-air.eth) Mixing by :DFACE, Marcus “Hardhead” Richard, JRich ENT, sayhellojordan, Sergio, T-Lay and werb Mastered by Sergio, Re:Send, sayhellojordan, :DFACE Cover art by J'von (aka Catman)
metadata.name: The Loser Club Mixtape Volume I
